 2023-03332023-04-20PWGSC
ActCanada Post Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of THOMAS ANTHONY RUTH of Edmonton, Alberta, to be a director of the Canada Post Corporation Board of Directors, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of James Hunter Sinclair, whose term has expired, effective April 21, 2023.
